    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "<strong>Note from Mozilla:</strong> This add-on has been discontinued. Try <a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/addon-update-checker/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Add-on Update Checker</a> instead.\n\nNotifies you when updates are available for your extensions and themes. Allows quick access to your extensions and themes and the ability to check both types for any updates. Easily configurable for automatically installing updates when available and checking for updates when Firefox starts."
    },
